Text.Value: How long have you been here?
Did True Soul Nere send you after the forge?
What is so special about the forge back there?
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*
Why aren't you helping dig out Nere?

EditorData.logicalname: Had mindmeld with Nere, still trapped

Text.Value: Don't care... about True Soul... only coin...

Synopsis: SwD with the Taskmaster in the Fearful Rothe situation. He might tell you about an ancient forge lying further inside Grymforge.
